  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/251/mode/1up">251</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/251/mode/1up">251</ref>.</p>
<p>ic cūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, mēṟ kūṟappaṭṭa avaṟṟukkellām potuvāyatōr puṟaṉaṭai uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.</p>
<p>varalāṟu : aḻāṉ, puḻāṉ eṉpaṉa ; akkālattu avai yuṇmaiyāṉ āciriyaṉ ōti muṭipu kūṟappaṭṭaṉa.</p>
<p>iṉic, cuṭṭucciṉai nīṭiya aikāravīṟṟup peyar (tol. eḻuttu. tokaimarapu - 17) uṟaḻntu muṭika eṉṟāṉ āciriyaṉ, ak kālattu avai yuṇmaiyāṉ ; ippoḻutu avaṟṟiṟku utāraṇamillai. piṟavum aṉṉa.</p>
<p>iṉi, āciriyaṉāl ākā eṉa ōtappaṭṭaṉa tōṉṟuva uḷa ; avai, ñeṇṭu eṉṟum, nīrkaṇṭaka eṉṟum, campu caḷḷai eṉṟum varum.	 (56)</p>

</body>
  </text>

